name: Crossroads
description: Skyward view of a corner in downtown São Paulo (coordinates: -23.543892, -46.640065), composited from two pictures taken with an ultrawideangle lens (10mm at f10). Date of capture 6 September 2014. Originally released as HeN OBJKT 51581 on 27 April 2021. Completely reprocessed from the source files with much higher quality for this re-release.
